item.title: 【Unreleased/Unofficial (lossy)】MP3 - Mariah Carey - The Rarities (Lambily Edition)
item.description:
​

The Rarities (Lambily Edition) is a fanmade compilation of songs by Mariah Carey. It was uploaded to several sharing sites sometime in 2008, and features a mix of b-sides, demos, live tracks, and unreleased songs recorded by Carey from the late 1980's (prior to her official debut) until the E=MC2 (2008) era.

2. Everytime
3. Weakness of the Body (Final Demo)
4. Don't Play That Song (For Me) [Live]
5. I'll Be There (Studio Recording) [feat. Trey Lorenz]

8. Just Be Good to Me (Live)

13. Never Too Far/Hero Medley
